{"word":"G4649 - σκοπός - skopós - skop-os' - Mark","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκοπός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>skopós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>skop-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Mark"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"இலக்கு - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. an observer, a watchman"},{"paragraph":"2. the distant mark looked at, the goal or end one has in view"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (&ldquo;scope&rdquo;); From <b>&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>skeptomai</b> (to <i>peer</i> about [&ldquo;skeptic&rdquo;]; perhaps akin to <a href=\"#/G4626 - σκάπτω - skáptō - skap'-to/4626\">G4626</a> through the idea of <i>concealment</i>; compare <a href=\"#/G4629 - σκέπασμα - sképasma - skep'-as-mah/4629\">G4629</a>); a <i>watch</i> (<i>sentry</i> or <i>scout</i>), that is, (by implication) a <i>goal:</i> - mark."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2684 - κατασκοπέω - kataskopéō - kat-as-kop-eh'-o/2684\">G2684</a>, <a href=\"#/G2685 - κατάσκοπος - katáskopos - kat-as'-kop-os/2685\">G2685</a>, <a href=\"#/G4648 - σκοπέω - skopéō - skop-eh'-o/4648\">G4648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4649 - σκοπός - skopós - skop-os'/4649\">G4649</a>"}]}